    <section class="featured">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <hgroup class="title">
                <h1>WELCOME TO BEAVER SPORTS</h1>
                <h2></h2>
            </hgroup>
            <p><strong>Beaver Sports was established in 1982 in Huddersfield, West Yorkshire and has grown to become one of the Europe&rsquo;s leading and most respected suppliers and manufacturers of diving equipment. We have achieved this by supplying the highest quality diving equipment and providing the highest levels of first class customer care. Our all new website has a completely fresh and modern look, assisting us to remain market leaders and also ensure that customers can easily find their requirements and also discover the latest innovations in the SCUBA industry. </strong></p>

<p><strong>Beaver Sports supply hundreds of dive shops around the world, details can be found on the &#39;<a href="/Home/Dealers/UK">UK Dealers</a>&#39; and &#39;<a href="/Home/Dealers/International">World Dealers</a>&#39; section. In addition to our website we also have a Facebook page,&nbsp;which is&nbsp;an ever growing source of up to date information,&nbsp;product development and news. To join the many others who visit us regularly, simply click on the Facebook logo at the bottom of this page.</strong></p>

<p><strong>HOW TO ORDER</strong></p>

<p><strong>Once you have found the item you wish to purchase from our extensive range, simply locate your nearest dive store using the &#39;<a href="/Home/Dealers/UK">UK Dealers</a>&#39; or &#39;<a href="/Home/Dealers/International">World Dealers</a>&#39; link and contact them with your needs quoting our product reference code. If you require any help, further information or to check availability please contact us on 01484-512354 or <a href="mailto:sales@beaversports.co.uk">sales@beaversports.co.uk</a> for assistance. We also operate an efficient mail order service, should you have any difficulty.</strong></p>

<p><strong>DEALERS</strong></p>

<p><strong>All Beaver products are available through our approved retailers, conveniently located throughout the UK,&nbsp;Europe and many other parts of the world. Should you require assistance and your local dealer is unable to help, please contact us directly. We are proud of the skills, knowledge and customer service that our experienced staff and dealers maintain. We&nbsp;look forward to hearing from you.</strong></p>

        </div>
    </section>

